name: Nanas Cake
desc: A cake with a fascinating shape. Mix the paste well, then place into a mold and heat until fully cooked. The edges are particularly susceptible to burning. If you're looking for a perfect golden color on your Nanas Cake, the most important thing is to control the heat.

value.text: Increases all party members' ATK by 194 for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
